{
  "id": "69b865360e66e71eaf8f3346",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:翻訳者は裏切り者",
  "created": 1773692241,
  "updated": 1773693136,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b865360e66e71eaf8f3346",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:翻訳者は裏切り者",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692241,
      "updated": 1773692241
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865510000000000d1c74b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692241,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c74c",
      "text": "ねえねえ今日のテーマ、「[翻訳者は裏切り者]」ってやつ！　なんか物騒ワードきたｗ　でもゲームとかアニメの翻訳見てると、たしかに「え、それ意訳すぎない？」って思うことあるんだよね～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c74d",
      "text": "この言葉、もともとはイタリア語のことわざ「Traduttore, traditore（翻訳者は裏切り者）」らしいよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c74e",
      "text": "じゃ、まず二人どう思う？　翻訳って裏切りなの？🤔",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c74f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c750",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c751",
      "text": "まあ……なんだか、少し胸がきゅっとする言葉ですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c752",
      "text": "翻訳とは、本来ひとつの言葉の世界を、別の言葉の世界へと渡す橋のような営みでしょう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c753",
      "text": "けれど橋を架けるとき、川の流れも、岸の形も、まったく同じにはできません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c754",
      "text": "ですから……原文の香りや響きが、ほんの少し変わってしまうことは、避けがたいのかもしれませんわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c755",
      "text": "裏切りというより、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c756",
      "text": "「別の国の空気をまとわせて生まれ直す」ようなことではないかしら。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c757",
      "text": "（静かに微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c758",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c759",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c75a",
      "text": "概念を整理しよう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c75b",
      "text": "「翻訳者は裏切り者」という言葉は、翻訳における不可避な情報損失を指摘したものだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c75c",
      "text": "言語には以下の層がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c75d",
      "text": " 1. 語彙（単語の意味）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c75e",
      "text": " 2. 文法構造",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c75f",
      "text": " 3. 文化的背景",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c760",
      "text": " 4. 音やリズム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c761",
      "text": "このうち 3. と 4. は特に翻訳が難しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c762",
      "text": "例えばジョーク。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c763",
      "text": "文化依存なので直訳すると意味不明になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c764",
      "text": "結果として翻訳者は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c765",
      "text": " 直訳 → 意味が伝わらない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c766",
      "text": " 意訳 → 原文から離れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c767",
      "text": "このトレードオフに常に直面する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c768",
      "text": "要点：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c769",
      "text": " 完全な翻訳は理論上ほぼ不可能",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c76a",
      "text": " だから「裏切り」という比喩が生まれた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c76b",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c76c",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traduttore,_traditore",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c76d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c76e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c76f",
      "text": "あーそれそれ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c770",
      "text": "直訳か意訳か問題ねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c771",
      "text": "ゲームのローカライズとかマジそれじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c772",
      "text": "たとえばさ、海外ゲームで",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c773",
      "text": "「Holy crap!」みたいなのを",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c774",
      "text": "「なんてこった！」とかにするじゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c775",
      "text": "でもそのまま",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c776",
      "text": "「聖なるクソ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c777",
      "text": "とかやったら完全にギャグｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c778",
      "text": "だから翻訳者って、[** 裏切りっていうか…調整役？] って感じするなあ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c779",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c77a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c77b",
      "text": "そうですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c77c",
      "text": "翻訳者は、まるで……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c77d",
      "text": "二つの言葉の国のあいだに立つ旅人のようです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c77e",
      "text": "どちらの国の人々にも理解されるよう、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c77f",
      "text": "時には言葉を置き換え、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c780",
      "text": "時には意味をやさしくほどいて渡す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c781",
      "text": "もしそれを「裏切り」と呼ぶなら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c782",
      "text": "それはきっと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c783",
      "text": "誰かに届くための小さな裏切りなのではないでしょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c784",
      "text": "（少し考え込む）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c785",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c786",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c787",
      "text": "文学では特に顕著だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c788",
      "text": "有名な例として、村上春樹の翻訳がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c789",
      "text": "彼はレイモンド・チャンドラーなどを翻訳している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c78a",
      "text": "彼の翻訳はかなり意訳寄りだと言われる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c78b",
      "text": "だが、その結果として日本語としてのリズムが成立する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c78c",
      "text": "つまり翻訳には二つの哲学がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c78d",
      "text": " 1. 忠実性（faithfulness）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773693130
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c78e",
      "text": "  原文に近づける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c78f",
      "text": " 2. 可読性（readability）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773693136
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c790",
      "text": "  読者に自然に伝える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c791",
      "text": "この最適点を探すのが翻訳者の仕事。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c792",
      "text": "要点をまとめる：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c793",
      "text": " 翻訳＝情報変換",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c794",
      "text": " 完全再現は不可能",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c795",
      "text": " だから翻訳者は「解釈者」でもある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c796",
      "text": "少し中二的に言うなら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c797",
      "text": "翻訳者は言語世界を横断するインターフェースだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c798",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c799",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c79a",
      "text": "出たｗ りかの中二テック用語ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c79b",
      "text": "でもさー、ちょっと思うんだけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c79c",
      "text": "翻訳者って作品の第二の作者っぽくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c79d",
      "text": "だって翻訳でキャラの口調とか変わるじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c79e",
      "text": "アニメの字幕とか吹き替えとか、全然印象違うし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c79f",
      "text": "あやはどう思う？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a2",
      "text": "そうですわね……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a3",
      "text": "翻訳された物語を読むとき、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a4",
      "text": "わたくしたちは実は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a5",
      "text": "作者と翻訳者、二人の声を重ねて聞いているのかもしれません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a6",
      "text": "原作者が灯した物語の灯りを、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a7",
      "text": "翻訳者がそっと別のランプに移し替える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a8",
      "text": "その灯りの色が、ほんの少し変わることもあるでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7a9",
      "text": "けれど灯りが消えてしまうより、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7aa",
      "text": "遠くの人へ届く方が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7ab",
      "text": "きっと物語も喜ぶのではないでしょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7ac",
      "text": "（やわらかく微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7ae",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7af",
      "text": "結論を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b0",
      "text": "「翻訳者は裏切り者」という言葉の本質は、批判ではなくパラドックスだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b1",
      "text": " 原文に忠実なら読者に伝わらない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b2",
      "text": " 読者に合わせると原文から離れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b3",
      "text": "つまり翻訳者は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b4",
      "text": "裏切らないと伝えられない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b5",
      "text": "という矛盾を背負っている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b8",
      "text": "おー、今日のまとめ出た！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7b9",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7ba",
      "text": " 翻訳は完全コピーじゃない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7bb",
      "text": " ちょっと変わるのは仕方ない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7bc",
      "text": " むしろそれで別の文化に届く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7bd",
      "text": "ってことだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7be",
      "text": "「裏切り」っていうより、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7bf",
      "text": "言葉の世界をつなぐバグ修正パッチみたいなもんかもｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7c0",
      "text": "今日の鼎談、こんな感じでどう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7c1",
      "text": "みんなおつ～！ 🎮📚💻",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865520000000000d1c7c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692242,
      "updated": 1773692242
    },
    {
      "id": "69b865540000000000d1c7c3",
      "text": "#2026-03-17",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692244,
      "updated": 1773692256
    },
